| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3315 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: daecaa09-f7ba-5ec7-8d86-53113f6d08eb"
